OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780074357
OL,3,CTeenage boy arrested after throwing a
OL,4,Cmachete into a nearby garden
OL,6,FA boy aged just 14 has been arrested
OL,7,Fafter a machete and 74 wraps of
OL,8,Fsuspected crack cocaine and heroin
OL,9,Fwere found in Bootle.
OL,11,FThe teenager had run away from police
OL,12,Fofficers in the early hours of 28 May,
OL,13,Fand thrown the machete into a nearby
OL,14,Fgarden.
OL,16,FMerseyside Police also found a snap
OL,17,Fbag of white powder suspected to be
OL,18,FKetamine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
