PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780074357
OL,3,CTeenage boy arrested after throwing a
OL,4,Cmachete into a nearby garden
OL,6,FThe boy, from Bootle, was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of carrying a bladed article
OL,8,Fin a public place and possession with
OL,9,Fthe intent to supply crack cocaine and
OL,10,Fheroin.
OL,12,FHe was taken to a police station in
OL,13,FMerseyside and remains in custody.
OL,15,FSefton Area Commander Karl Baldwin
OL,16,Fsaid: "To carry such a dangerous
OL,17,Fweapon and discard it in someone's
OL,18,Fgarden is completely reckless
OL,19,Fbehaviour that will not be tolerated
OL,20,Fon our streets, regardless of the age
OL,21,Fof the person responsible.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
