OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780074357
OL,3,CTeenage boy arrested after throwing a
OL,4,Cmachete into a nearby garden
OL,6,F"These types of weapons have no place
OL,7,Fin Sefton, and neither do the people
OL,8,Fprepared to carry them who put
OL,9,Fthemselves and others at risk of harm.
OL,11,F"Our officers have also seized a
OL,12,Fsignificant amount of illicit drugs
OL,13,Fthat could have caused serious harm in
OL,14,Four community.
OL,16,F"If you know anyone who is carrying,
OL,17,Fusing, or storing drugs or weapons,
OL,18,Fplease come forward so we can continue
OL,19,Fto disrupt offenders and bring them to
OL,20,Fjustice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU|D@IO]
